title: United Kingdom Imports - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coins
description: Imports - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coins in the United Kingdom decreased to 3650.95 GBP Million in September from 4639.72 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coins in the United Kingdom averaged 2354.03 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 12020.71 GBP Million in September of 2020 and a record low of 337.51 GBP Million in September of 2002. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Pearls, Precious Stones & Metals & Coi.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
